# Vending System CLI

## 📌 Overview
The Vending System CLI is a Python-based command-line application that simulates a real-world vending machine. It handles product selection, stock management, payment processing, and transaction logging.

---

## 🎯 Purpose
This project demonstrates core programming concepts such as:
- Control flow
- User input validation
- File handling
- Basic system design

---

## ⚙️ Features
- Product selection via command-line interface
- Stock validation and management
- Payment simulation with change calculation
- Transaction logging system

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack
- Python

---

## 🚀 How to Run
```bash
python src/main.py
